<plot>The smalls...er whatever charts the highs and lows of Alberta rock cowboys the smalls as they cross Canada and tour France and Belgium for the first time. Features European riot footage, backstage antics, studio recording footage from 1998's My Dear Little Angle, van breakdowns and band fights in France. Features the smalls rock classics: Payload, PIN, My SaddleHorse has Died, and Alvarez.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?591563</url></doc>
